MAil-SendGrid-SmtpApiHeader
===========================

This module provides a simple way to generate the custom SMTP extension header used by
SendGrid.

See the file "Changes" for all changes made to this software.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries at runtime:

  JSON

